{"tid":242600,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"整荼樓點心比老母食，點知比佢罵我小家","createTime":"2017-05-14T04:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T04:32:45.000Z","uid":8883,"like":134,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a566749b5946ded8e80fe73212d2e3dbaa57ca84","tid":242600,"uid":8883,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"年年老母節 老母都會神咁早7點就叫全家去飲荼 <br />\n仲要次次屈9我比 +專登叫埋哂d特點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當正自己係老母就大哂咁 兒童節又唔見兒童大哂?fuck <br />\n<br />\n咁我岩岩考完DSE 日日都同D fd子出街玩 <br />\n又未搵到署期工 邊有咁多閒錢請老母飲荼呀 <br />\n3條友加埋 起碼都要200蚊埋單啦 <br />\n仲要老母節收得特別貴tim D荼樓正一Hi Hi黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗到條屎橋 親手下廚扮孝順 又可以慳返d錢 <br />\n結果6點半起身就開始整啦 <br />\n<br />\n食材如下: <br />\n<img src=\"http://doll.com.hk:8080/doll/images/products/Frozen%20Food/Doll%20Dim%20Sum/FF13029ShrimpShaoMai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdoll.com.hk%3A8080%2Fdoll%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2FFrozen%2520Food%2FDoll%2520Dim%2520Sum%2FFF13029ShrimpShaoMai.jpg&h=bdd4c0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.aeoncity.com.hk/ShareLibrary/product_image/002182152/002182152-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aeoncity.com.hk%2FShareLibrary%2Fproduct_image%2F002182152%2F002182152-1.jpg&h=72f977a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n蝦餃燒賣呢d就基本啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/shrimpsalad81/1211563431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fshrimpsalad81%2F1211563431.jpg&h=6e2c4637&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/shrimpsalad81/1211563431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fshrimpsalad81%2F1211563431.jpg&h=6e2c4637&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.aeoncity.com.hk/ShareLibrary/product_image/002908150/002908150-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aeoncity.com.hk%2FShareLibrary%2Fproduct_image%2F002908150%2F002908150-1.jpg&h=69645a42&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n包類就易塞飽老母個肚 所以整三包 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.daihung.com/photos/DSC02365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.daihung.com%2Fphotos%2FDSC02365.jpg&h=030f7b00&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n珍珠雞就貴野黎既 平時飲荼好少叫 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www1.parknshop.com/WebShop/images/prd/139784_l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.parknshop.com%2FWebShop%2Fimages%2Fprd%2F139784_l.gif&h=237111f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老母平時鐘意食粥 所以特意買多碗粥 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ccue.com/tor/hotdeals/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/20110329-093217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccue.com%2Ftor%2Fhotdeals%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F03%2F20110329-093217.jpg&h=729e7652&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ccue.com/tor/hotdeals/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/20110329-093217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccue.com%2Ftor%2Fhotdeals%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F03%2F20110329-093217.jpg&h=729e7652&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n麵就我自己食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ssc.com.hk/bookpic3/722020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ssc.com.hk%2Fbookpic3%2F722020.jpg&h=c6904315&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最後再沖埋香片 咁先match返去荼樓飲茶果種感覺 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就滿心歡喜 叫老母起身飲荼 <br />\n點知老母一見到D點心就話我小家 串我請一餐荼都唔肯 <br />\n我咪同佢嘈 :依家咪請你飲荼囉 有乜分別呀 點解你咁貪慕虛榮一定要食大荼樓~ <br />\n<br />\n都唔知係咪佢陳晚打麻雀輸錢 搵我黎出氣 <br />\n猛咁話生叉燒好過生我 仲拎d叉燒包掉我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我慶慶地(D包好向左走向右走熱) 拎返D燒賣掉佢還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻話以後唔比零用錢我 之後沖左落街 (我估佢係去打麻雀) <br />\n<br />\n結果得返老豆同埋我 食哂D點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n谷勁向左走向右走氣 天日仲約左fd子唱k d錢用左黎買點心 依家都唔知點算..."},{"pid":"21413e390dd5d50613eb0c3bfde3fa820d778aec","tid":242600,"uid":29987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5609b4a967bbb9116c58e8ba671dfdd8f032179d","tid":242600,"uid":39080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"幾好笑 俾個正評你啦"},{"pid":"6bc73f62d9df7150a20ac655a3cc28f6eaeadd62","tid":242600,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"Loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e34ecb742ebe4b32118f3dfffba2a8498acc22e","tid":242600,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"咪就係，茶樓飲茶好揾笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5830aa2a3ab53482c3eb049c68736e8abf04cf2b","tid":242600,"uid":65437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961baa75f820a1bd445ff87b97e616fc4d36af76","tid":242600,"uid":78175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bcb38b50f865dce0e87399cbcc64bef97cc23f0","tid":242600,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"又想釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e766206f537a0db81c29a56cbcf6cee880bcab28","tid":242600,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"父親節版本好笑啲<br />\n特別係執返啲叉燒黎食個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365c8016aeb819ca6dd0fe40679592a5edb785ae","tid":242600,"uid":84895,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"次次睇呢篇野見到個荼字都覺得好撚唔舒服<br />\n<span style=